    H["POST /api/internal-data/retrieve\nsrc/backend/routers/internal_data.py::retrieve_data"] -->|"Trigger: retrieval request\nData: InternalDataRetrieveRequest(query, limit)\nWhy: run semantic top-k lookup with stable API shape"| I["src/backend/services/internal_data_service.py::retrieve_internal_data"]
    I -->|"Trigger: db dialect == postgresql\nData: query_embedding + cosine_distance ORDER BY + LIMIT\nWhy: rank top-k directly in database using pgvector operator"| K["Postgres SQL similarity ranking\ninternal_data_service.retrieve_internal_data"]
    K -->|"Data moved: chunk_id/document_id/title/source_type/source_ref/content + distance\nWhy: preserve retrieval schema while converting distance -> score"| L["InternalDataRetrieveResponse.results"]
